some strong language.

00:10.800 --> 00:13.040
Are you going to behave for me
on this flight?

00:14.200 --> 00:15.720
Yes, you are.

00:17.720 --> 00:19.120
You cheeky little monkey.

00:20.360 --> 00:25.020
You are a cheeky little monkey.

00:27.469 --> 00:29.580
