Peter.

00:43.840 --> 00:47.104
Jo, this is Peter,
we went to school together.

00:47.105 --> 00:48.640
- He's a detective.
- I'm so sorry.

00:50.280 --> 00:51.879
You've spoken with the officers?

00:51.880 --> 00:53.280
Yeah.

00:55.000 --> 00:56.519
Dad!

00:56.520 --> 00:58.000
Chlo.

